snippet.title: DAREDEVIL: BORN AGAIN Season 2 Official Teaser Trailer (2026) Marvel
snippet.description:
Official Daredevil: Born Again Series Teaser Trailer 2026 | More ➤ https://KinoCheck.com/App | Charlie Cox Series Trailer | Disney+: 24 Mar 2026 | Details ➤ https://KinoCheck.com/show/1wc/daredevil-born-again-2025?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=description
A new Disney+ series with Matt Murdock aka Daredevil from the Marvel Cinematic Universe. The plot around Daredevil, Kingpin and the Punisher is supposed to take over parts of the old series, but to rewrite some of the story elements.

Daredevil: Born Again (2026) is the new action series starring Charlie Cox, Vincent D'Onofrio and Michael Gandolfini.
